@BioTime_HostAddress = http://localhost:5286

### Listar empleados (paginado)
GET {{BioTime_HostAddress}}/api/biotime/employees?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Obtener empleado por ID
GET {{BioTime_HostAddress}}/api/biotime/employees/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear empleado
POST {{BioTime_HostAddress}}/api/biotime/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "empCode": "EMP001",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "lastName": "Perez",
  "department": 1,
  "position": 1,
  "hireDate": "2026-01-15"
}

### Actualizar empleado
PUT {{BioTime_HostAddress}}/api/biotime/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "empCode": "EMP001",
  "firstName": "Juan Carlos",
  "lastName": "Perez Lopez",
  "department": 1,
  "position": 2,
  "hireDate": "2026-01-15"
}

### Eliminar empleado
DELETE {{BioTime_HostAddress}}/api/biotime/employees/1
Accept: application/json

